Plugin Installation:

In a web browser open STASH_URL/plugins/servlet/upm#manage
Click Upload add-on
Choose the attached .jar file.
Plugin is activated.

When first started, plugin disables Private Repositories for every user.
To enable private repositories to some groups you have to

Log in as an administrator.
Go to administration.
Select "Private Repositories" from left hand menu.
You can search and add single users as well as groups who can access private repositories here.